    "Very nice place.",
    "Dense pine forest on the west side of the peak of Tossa d'Incles. A nice hiking route along the lower slopes of the beautiful Vall d'Incles.",
    "In a natural depression at the foot of Tossa d'Incles you reach two small mountain ponds that collect meltwater.",
    "Beautiful mountain pass at 2,572 meters above sea level, which connects the Gros river valley and the Estany de Siscaró along the hiking section of the GRP Volta a Andorra.",
    "Rising above the Vall d'Incles, the route climbs above the lakes of Siscaró and reaches the top of Tossa d'Incles at 2569 masl."
